ialwissenschaftler und andere Spezialisten erforschen Modelle für eine saubere, sichere, umwelt- und ressourcenschonende Stadt.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin:14px;background:#fff;width:276px;\">\r\n<p><img src=\"/system/images/W1siZiIsIjIwMTQvMDMvMTQvMTRfMDlfNTRfMTM1X3NodXR0ZXJzdG9ja182MDY3Njg5MV8zMjB4MTIwLmpwZyJdXQ/shutterstock_60676891_320x120.jpg\" title=\"Shutterstock 60676891 320x120\" alt=\"Shutterstock 60676891 320x120\" data-rel=\"450x450\" width=\"276\" height=\"104\" />\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"width:235px;padding:10px;\">\r\n<p><strong>Materialforschung</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"color_blue\" style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:30px;\"><strong>Clevere Kunststoffe</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Forscher tüfteln an Materialien mit Formgedächtnis. Was bisher nur mit speziellen Metalllegierungen möglich war, soll künftig auch mit Kunststoffen funktionieren</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n'),(51,51,'en','2014-03-12 08:50:38','2014-03-12 08:50:38',''),(52,52,'en','2014-03-12 08:50:38','2014-03-12 08:50:38',''),(53,53,'en','2014-03-12 08:51:10','2014-03-12 08:51:10',''),(54,54,'en','2014-03-12 08:51:10','2014-03-12 08:51:10',''),(55,55,'en','2014-03-12 08:51:22','2014-03-12 08:51:22',''),(56,56,'en','2014-03-12 08:51:22','2014-03-12 08:51:22',''),(57,57,'en','2014-03-12 08:51:34','2014-03-12 08:51:34',''),(58,58,'en','2014-03-12 08:51:34','2014-03-12 08:51:34',''),(59,59,'en','2014-03-12 08:51:45','2014-03-12 08:51:45',''),(60,60,'en','2014-03-12 08:51:45','2014-03-12 08:51:45',''),(63,63,'en','2014-03-12 08:52:13','2014-03-12 08:52:13',''),(64,64,'en','2014-03-12 08:52:13','2014-03-12 08:52:13',''),(65,65,'en','2014-03-12 08:53:06','2014-03-12 08:53:06',''),(66,66,'en','2014-03-12 08:53:06','2014-03-12 08:53:06',''),(67,67,'en','2014-03-12 08:53:55','2014-03-12 08:53:55',''),(68,68,'en','2014-03-12 08:53:55','2014-03-12 08:53:55',''),(69,69,'en','2014-03-12 08:54:07','2014-03-12 08:54:07',''),(70,70,'en','2014-03-12 08:54:07','2014-03-12 08: